# Specialists directory

Dynamically created agents live here, one directory per specialist.

Naming: project-scoped, descriptive, short (e.g., `figma-expert/`, `stripe-billing/`).

Each specialist directory should contain:
- `SKILL.md` — role, scope, decline/escalate triggers
- Any helper scripts or configs
- A `lessons-learned.md` linking back to entries in `../../lessons-learned/`

Specialists are terminated at end of project lifecycle. Their lessons-learned persist.
